list.name: Changes
list.comment: Two stacks are created. Enter the number or negative number entered by the user. In the while loop, if the integer is greater than 0, it goes to the driveway stack. If it is less than 0, driveway.pop. I wrote a method called "CarMoveToStreet". It can be realized that when the number is less than 0, the car will be popped out of the driveway stack, the corresponding number will be removed, and then the remaining cars will be returned from the streetway to the driveway stack.
